text: Has anyone else on Rdio had a weird phantom voice interfere over top of your music? It just happened to me for the second time. I rewind and it isn't there anymore. I think dead people are trying to speak to me.
Does it sound like a taxi/cop radio?
i recently thought i heard a voice over a song, telling me quietly to kill myself. but then i listened to the song again and it was still there.
Maybe. It's usually over louder parts so I can't pick out what it's saying.
on second listen, the meaning may have changed. the first time i heard the voice i wasn't exactly sober.
we can help investigate this for you
it was Alaskans, by Volcano Choir. The voice comes in near the end, starting at 3:53
the VO is an excerpt from The Shower, by Bukowski. <http://allpoetry.com/poem/8509525-The-Shower-by-Charles-Bukowski>
But which poet is speaking to me from beyond the grave though?
shoulda known it was bukowski. It's always bukowski.
